---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { Container } from "@/components/layout/Container";
import HeroImage from "../components/ui/HeroImage.astro";
import { ArrowRight } from "lucide-react";
---

<Layout
    title="Cost of Starting a Daycare | Childcare Business Plan"
    description="Daycare startup costs vary dramatically by state, facility type, and local regulations. Get personalized insights for your situation."
>
    <!-- HERO SECTION -->
    <section class="pro-section">
        <Container size="md">
            <HeroImage
                src="/images/startup/cost-of-starting-a-daycare.webp"
                alt="Financial planning dashboard highlighting the typical cost to open a daycare in various markets"
                className="mb-4 md:mb-12"
            />
            <div class="text-center">
                <span class="pro-text-meta mb-2 block">
                    Startup Investment
                </span>
                <h1 class="text-xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2 md:mb-6">
                    YOUR Startup Investment
                </h1>
                <p class="text-sm md:text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
                    The cost to start a daycare isn't a fixed number—it's a range that depends on your state's requirements, your facility type, and the scale of your launch.
                </p>
            </div>
        </Container>
    </section>

    <!-- FACTORS SECTION -->
    <section class="pro-section bg-gray-50/50">
        <Container size="md">
            <div class="pro-card mb-3 md:mb-8">
                <h2 class="text-base md:text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2 md:mb-6 uppercase tracking-wider">
                    What Affects Your Costs
                </h2>
                <div class="space-y-3 text-xs md:text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed font-medium">
                    <p>
                        Starting costs vary by orders of magnitude. A home-based family daycare might require a few thousand dollars in modifications. A center-based program could require tens of thousands for facility buildout.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        State and local regulations drive many of these costs. Some jurisdictions require extensive modifications, specialized equipment, or specific square footage per child. 
                    </p>
                    <p class="hidden md:block">
                        Your timeline affects costs too. Rushing means paying premium prices for contractors and expedited licensing. A longer runway lets you find better deals.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </Container>
    </section>

    <!-- WHY GENERIC FAILS SECTION -->
    <section class="pro-section">
        <Container size="md">
            <div class="pro-card">
                <h2 class="text-base md:text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2 md:mb-6 uppercase tracking-wider">
                    Why Online Advice Conflicts
                </h2>
                <div class="space-y-3 text-xs md:text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed font-medium">
                    <p>
                        Search for costs and you'll find estimates from $3,000 to $300,000. Both might be accurate—for completely different scenarios. A home daycare looks nothing like a licensed center.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Generic breakdowns assume conditions that might not apply to you. You need to understand the cost drivers specific to your situation before you can budget accurately.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </Container>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA SECTION -->
    <section class="pro-section">
        <Container size="md">
            <div class="pro-card text-center border-2 border-teal-200/50 bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-50/20 to-white/50">
                <h2 class="text-base md:text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2 md:mb-4">
                    Calculate YOUR Startup Costs
                </h2>
                <p class="text-xs md:text-base text-gray-600 mb-3 md:mb-6">
                    Understand your income potential and startup investment before you commit.
                </p>
                <a
                    href="/#calculator"
                    class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 justify-center rounded-full bg-teal-600 hover:bg-teal-700 text-white font-bold px-5 py-2 md:px-8 md:py-4 shadow-lg transition-all text-xs md:text-base group"
                >
                    Use the Free Calculator
                    <ArrowRight className="w-3.5 h-3.5 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform" />
                </a>
            </div>
        </Container>
    </section>
</Layout>
